title: One Story Home with 4 Bedrooms! Fenced yard plus Fenced wood deck!
posting_body: ['**Attached link to our website with more information and photos, please copy and paste the link**', '<URL>', 'Right in the heart of Yelm, great location!', 'One story home with 4 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms with attached 2 car garage and fenced backyard!', 'Front entrance has a wood deck great for morning coffee, backyard has a nice large wood deck that is fully fenced for barbecues and entertainment!', 'Easy backyard to maintain.', 'Walk through kitchen is spacious with plenty of cabinets for storage.', 'Kitchen opens up to dining and a large living room great for entertaining.', 'Large master bedroom with walk in closet and attached bathroom.', 'Close to JBLM, schools and shopping.', 'Non Refundable pet deposit of $500 per pet and pet rent is $25 per pet monthly.', 'Please submit an application on <URL>.', 'To schedule a showing the application needs to be approved.', 'Application fees non refundable.', 'Non refundable holding fee of (25% of rent) is due within 3 days of approved applications.']
